<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM5.3.4">
<l>ūravar kavvai yeruviṭ ṭaṉṉaico ṉīrmaṭut</l>
<l>tīranel vitti muḷaitta neñcap peruñceyyuḷ</l>
<l>pēramar kātal kaṭalpurai yaviḷai vitta</l>
<l>kāramar mēṉinaṅ kaṇṇaṉ ṭōḻī kaṭiyaṉē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>To ripen, like the ocean, great lasting love</l>
<l>in the big field of [my] heart that sprouted after sowing paddy of affection,</l>
<l>drinking in as water mother’s words, the villagers’ gossip putting manure,</l>
<l>harsh, friend, [is] our Kaṇṇaṉ, with a body like a monsoon cloud.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
